<br>
Can't help it, I'm used to it.  For years I've been the Officer in my guilds who people felt comfortable coming to when they had problems, because I never ignored them.<br>
<br>
In my time I've been a shoulder for discussions of sex, drugs, death, suicide, children, love, hate, marriage, divorce, domestic violence, depression, and anything else you can imagine.<br>
